{"tid":659394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食鬼亂煮系列---homemade cultured yogurt","createTime":"2018-05-09T19:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T17:56:00.000Z","uid":182683,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f6ccf3f048aec5b590ffa1f34ac0c2c33496d272","tid":659394,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T19:10:53.000Z","msg":"今次整d簡單野&mdash;乳酪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我日日都會食，但係香港買有D貴，好多加左糖，仲要有d成份都怪怪地(十幾樣野合成出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，有正常既不過貴(窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，greek yogurt再貴d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n我平時整開既乳酪得2種材料：奶同live cultures，最正就係整完第一次你就可以用整左個d剩係買奶無限整，五餅二魚大法！！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早餐栗米片x乳酪x蜜糖，好屈機呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/10/4hdRYv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F4hdRYv.jpg&h=93b50486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n牛奶 800g<br />\ncultured yogurt 40g(通常乳酪包裝背面寫住有live active yogurt cultures之類既字)<br />\n<br />\n做法：<br />\n1. 拎個煲磅奶(800g)，跟手用量杯磅埋乳酪(40g)(我用屋企食剩個樽)，份量差少少唔緊要，唔 好太離譜就得，如果想整多整少就自己計番個比例。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/10/A14JGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2FA14JGF.jpg&h=38b47d2a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/10/NIYqc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2FNIYqc8.jpg&h=5016ade8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 中細火將奶煮到83&deg;C(冇溫度計就煮到差唔多滾停)，中途一路攪住等佢唔好燶，如果你想有其他味道，就係依個時候落(茶/香料為主,係step4之前拎番走,最好唔好落水果,會令到製成品好水)，依個步驟會改變奶入面蛋白質令到個製成品更加杰同滑。<br />\n煮完攤凍到43&deg;C(冇溫度計用手摸,唔&rdquo;辣&rdquo;手就ok)，冚蓋漏少少空隙等佢唔會有層奶皮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/10/pSahx6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2FpSahx6.jpg&h=39ab870f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/10/yzD7lZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2FyzD7lZ.jpg&h=f21a3457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 倒少少奶落量杯溝稀d乳酪先，確保一定要撈得好混沌，唔好有細細粒既乳酪未溝混，之後倒曬所有奶溝混，入樽冚蓋。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/10/m4xYVj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2Fm4xYVj.jpg&h=8c7a68dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/10/K1fPJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2FK1fPJQ.jpg&h=9584b1ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 發酵有2種方法：1.好似我咁Sous vide，校43&deg;C放曬入去等5個鐘，我通常放過夜唔理；2.整一個接近43&deg;C既空間，我建議裝幾樽熱水冚蓋放入保溫箱/焗爐開住燈，放d奶入去直到凝固，大概時間話唔到你聽，視乎你溫度如何不過通常1日到，sous vide一定係最快同最穩定。<br />\nsous vide既人可以自己試下校唔同溫度，校低溫放長d時間(eg. 32&deg;C/15hrs)出到黎會再杰d，自己實驗下。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/10/xY1uL0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2FxY1uL0.jpg&h=96c3f326&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/10/pz03oc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2Fpz03oc.jpg&h=9190cb27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.成功左未食得住，要放雪櫃雪一晚先，我諗冇人會熱食乳酪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n如果鍾意greek yogurt既人，可以買煲湯袋剪開一半，放係篩上面，再倒乳酪上去由佢係雪櫃慢慢隔過夜，滴完份量會少左一半，但係會變到勁杰好似greek yogurt。我自己就唔會隔，隔完個d乳清勁難飲，唔知可以拎黎做咩😂 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/10/U2Aiqx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2FU2Aiqx.jpg&h=dde7dde3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白雪雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/10/OiNYqL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2FOiNYqL.jpg&h=e4dac864&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nig:hkfoodghost<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2bceea3e1cf42053cad8f176d18449696a4c26","tid":659394,"uid":12094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T21:28:42.000Z","msg":"唔錯   支持下你啦   <br />\n(之後我想講用麵包機都好似可以做到yogurt 放哂D料禁個制  唔洗幾個鐘就有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"62d9c1ee3ec6798f12bd411bc74596261c0baec4","tid":659394,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d2bceea3e1cf42053cad8f176d18449696a4c26","tid":659394,"uid":12094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T21:28:42.000Z","msg":"唔錯   支持下你啦   <br />\n(之後我想講用麵包機都好似可以做到yogurt 放哂D料禁個制  唔洗幾個鐘就有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T17:56:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/659396/page/3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/659396/page/3</a> &lt;&lt;依個先係原po<br />\n唔小心開多左個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}